article.description: — Christian Anigwe scored 14 points and UC Davis beat NAIA-member UC Merced 81-40 on Saturday.
article.headline: UC Davis upends NAIA-member Cal Merced 81-40
article.linkText: UC Davis upends NAIA-member Cal Merced 81-40
article.story: DAVIS, Calif. -- — Christian Anigwe scored 14 points and UC Davis beat NAIA-member UC Merced 81-40 on Saturday. The Aggies (4-3) built a 10-0 lead, extended it to 27-9 and went to intermission up 42-17. Leo DeBruhl, Kane Milling and Elijah Pepper each scored 11. Mason Westlake scored 11 points for the Bobcats. ------
